---
title: Thai 'Pad Krapow Moo' with Green Beans and Cilantro
description: Pad krapow moo is a popular dish in the Thai street food scene. Ground pork is stir-fried with aromatic ingredients such as ginger, garlic, lime and chili pepper and then served over fluffy rice.
